A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 3 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to state
2 flag, seal, and other symbols, so as to provide for placement of a Revolutionary War Patriots
3 marker upon the grounds of the state capitol building and upon the grounds of the state
4 archives building; to provide for the approval, placement, and procurement of such markers;
5 to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Chapter 3 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to state flag, seal,
9 and other symbols, is amended by adding a new article to read as follows:
10 "ARTICLE 8
11 50-3-130.
12 (a) There shall be placed upon the grounds of the state capitol building and upon the
13 grounds outside the state archives building a marker which commemorates the patriots of
14 the Revolutionary War, honoring the men and women who helped America achieve
